            (word)))

            (identifier)
            (identifier)))

          (parenthesized_rule
            (choice
              (word)
              (word))))))
    (command_block
      (expression_statement
        (action
          (action_identifier
            (identifier)
            (identifier))
          (argument_list
            (identifier)
            (string)))))))

    user.select_previous_occurrence(clip.text())
    sleep(100ms)
    edit.right()


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

(source_file
  (command
    (rule
      (seq
        (word)
        (word)
        (word)))
    (command_block
      (expression_statement
        (action
          (action_identifier
            (identifier)
            (identifier))
          (argument_list
            (action
              (action_identifier
                (identifier)
                (identifier))
              (argument_list)))))
      (expression_statement
        (sleep_action
          (implicit_string)))
      (expression_statement
        (action
          (action_identifier
            (identifier)
            (identifier))
          (argument_list))))))

    (rule
      (seq
        (parenthesized_rule
          (choice
            (word)
            (word)))
        (optional
          (word))
        (word)))
    (command_block
      (expression_statement
        (key_action
          (implicit_string))))))
